Title: Tunisia_GLCN
Organization: GLCN; Centre National de Teledetection de Tunisie
Notes: The GLCN initiative brings together national technical staff in the field of Remote Sensing/GIS
column16: and Food Security to develop a network at the regional and global scale to adopt the standardization of land cover measurement methods and develop regional and global land cover products. The collaboration involves not only data providers but also data users and policy-makers.
